<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Nangmah, bantuk, an umlo, khua ruahhar tuahtu
 Israel miphun chuahtu, dingah Moses cu
 Na thiang, thlarau, thawnnak in, Cannan ram leiah
 Minmei tom le, Mei tom in, lam hruaitu na si.

[C1]
   Bawipa, nangmah, bantuk an um lo
   Khua ruahhar, thil lianngan tuah kho tu
   Bawipa nangmah lawng.

[V2]
 Bawipa, nangmah lawng, khuaruah,
 Harnak tuah khotu
 Lungpi chungin, Tii a chuah, Ter khotu Bawipa
 Sunparnak le, Upatnak, Bawipa kan in pek
 Nangmah bantuk an umlo, khua ruahhar, tuah tu.</lyrics>
<key>E</key>
<title>NANGMAH BANTUK AN UM LO</title>
</song>